<div><head>周易上經</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1016_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1016_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1016_CHANT_001-1a.2">蒙</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1016_CHANT_001-1a.3">險而止，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1016_CHANT_001-1a.4">山也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1016_CHANT_001-1a.5">險而動，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1016_CHANT_001-1a.6">泉也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1016_CHANT_001-1a.7">動靜皆蒙險，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1016_CHANT_001-1a.8">故曰「山」。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1016_CHANT_001-1a.9">下缺，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1016_CHANT_001-1a.10">依文義當有「水蒙」二字。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1016_CHANT_001-1a.11">徐堅《初學記》卷五。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1016_CHANT_001-1a.12">《太平御覽》卷三十八。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
